questions.title: What tech is used for the app?
questions.text: The front end is written in react with typescript. The backend uses NodeJs, Express and Postgres

questions.title: How did you get the data for the game?
questions.text: Most of the data about ages, and number of episodes is from wikipedia. The number of dates is from re-watching. Instagram followers was collected manually and is correct as of april 2022. Terrace House Social was an invaluable resource to find everyone.

questions.title: Where can I add an issue I found in the game??
questions.text: Send us an email, or raise an issue in the github repo
